getLibraries

List<Sample> getLibraries()
Returns a complete list of libraries. A library is a particular kind of Sample that has been run or is eligible to run on a sequencer.

Returns:
All libraries.

getLibraries

List<Sample> getLibraries(Map<String,String> attributes)
Returns a list of libraries that match all attributes provided in the give attributes Map. Attributes may occur anywhere in the hierarchy, from the library itself all the way to the root.

Parameters:
attributes - A Map of attributes.
Returns:
A list of libraries.
